libglfx (0.51-0ubuntu6) oneiric; urgency=low

  * Update to r17.
 Cleanup of scanner.
 Restored single-to-multiline comments, since they're correct according to glsl spec. Though NVIDIA compiler doesn't handle them.
 Compilation warning fix.
 Bug fix. Scanner line reset on new file.

 -- Etay Meiri <etay.meiri@gmail.com>  Sun, 15 Jan 2012 20:20:56 +0200

